latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Learning to do makeup with one hand is a major mom hack!
Nostalgic about the time when I thought doing my makeup (with both hands and alone) in 10 min was my flex 🤐

PS: DONOT bring a mascara near your eye while holding your toddler! Yes, I learnt only after going almost half blind!
